From 1a163de0e5fb3e13c89210395e3a2f20e91c7ad7 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Carbonyl Maintainers <maintainers@carbonyl.dev>
Date: Fri, 26 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 33/33] carbonyl: enable promptless headless downloads

Install a headless DownloadManagerDelegate so downloads have a concrete target
path instead of being dropped by the default null delegate. The delegate honors
Chromium's --download-dir switch and falls back to a Downloads directory under
the browser context path when the switch is absent.

